&lt;p&gt;The Surgical Division at Worthing Hospital are looking for a full-time Support Secretary. The successful candidate will provide support across the General Surgery, Upper GI and Colorectal Teams. Applicants must be enthusiastic and hard-working, and able to contribute to a busy Team delivering a high level of administrative and secretarial support to the Team. Excellent interpersonal and typing skills, the ability to work under pressure and to be able to multi-task, as well as using their own initiative is essential to this post.&lt;/p&gt;
